<h1 class="text-3xl font-medium pt-4">Shipping Policy</h1>

<p class="mt-4">
  Last updated: <span class="text-green-400">10 Jun 2026</span>
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  We aim to process and dispatch orders as quickly as possible after payment has been successfully received.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  This Shipping Policy explains how orders are processed, shipped, and delivered.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Order Processing</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  Orders are typically processed within 1–3 business days. During busy periods, holidays, or promotional events,
  processing times may be slightly longer.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  Orders are not processed or shipped on weekends or public holidays.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Shipping Destinations</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  We ship to customers in many countries worldwide. Shipping availability and delivery times may vary depending on the
  destination.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  If we are unable to ship to your location, you will be notified during checkout or shortly after placing your order.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Estimated Delivery Times</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  Delivery times depend on your location, shipping carrier, customs procedures, and other factors outside our control.
</p>

<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4">
  <li>United Kingdom: typically 2–7 business days</li>
  <li>European Union: typically 5–14 business days</li>
  <li>International destinations: typically 7–21 business days</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-4">
  These delivery estimates are not guaranteed and should be considered approximate.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Tracking Information</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  Where available, tracking information will be provided once your order has been dispatched.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  Please allow up to 48 hours for tracking information to become active after shipment.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Customs, Duties, and Taxes</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  For international orders, customs duties, import taxes, VAT, and other fees may be charged by your local customs
  authority.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  These charges are the responsibility of the customer unless otherwise stated at checkout.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  We are not responsible for delays caused by customs inspections or import procedures.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Shipping Costs</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  Shipping costs are displayed during checkout before payment is completed.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  Where free shipping is offered, any applicable conditions will be clearly displayed on the website.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Incorrect Shipping Address</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  Customers are responsible for providing accurate shipping information.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  If you need to change your shipping address, please contact us as soon as possible at
  <a href="mailto:<%= site.email %>">
    <%= site.email %>
  </a>.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  Once an order has been shipped, we may be unable to modify the delivery address.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Lost, Delayed, or Missing Shipments</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  If your order has not arrived within the expected delivery period, please contact us and we will investigate the issue
  with the shipping carrier.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  While we will do our best to assist, we are not responsible for delays caused by circumstances beyond our control,
  including customs processing, weather conditions, transportation disruptions, or carrier-related issues.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Order Cancellations</h2>

<p class="mt-4">
  If you wish to cancel an order, please contact us as soon as possible at
  <a href="mailto:<%= site.email %>">
    <%= site.email %>
  </a>.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
  Orders that have already been processed or shipped may not be eligible for cancellation and may instead be subject to
  our Refund Policy.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6">Contact Us</h2>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  If you have any questions about shipping, delivery, or order status, please contact us:
  <br>
  <a href="mailto:<%= site.email %>">
    <%= site.email %>
  </a>
</p>
